{"tid":2394584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"金管局：銀公不接受BNO做開戶身份證明做法合適","createTime":"2021-02-04T09:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T13:09:42.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9d68abb3d5cdcf30d55426d43bed78d83e2c8a","tid":2394584,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:29:35.000Z","msg":"銀行公會說，不接受銀行客戶，以英國國民（海外）護照 BNO，作為開立戶口的有效身分證明文件。金管局副總裁阮國恒說，這個做法，是因應特區政府不承認BNO作為身分證明文件及旅遊證件，銀行公會有向局方諮詢意見，局方亦覺得做法合適。 阮國恒說，絕大部分香港居民都是以身分證開戶，如果只用BNO開戶，在更新資料時可能要提供其他身分證明文件。 對於虛擬銀行發展，阮國恒說，現時共有42萬個開戶，當局沒有特定指標，整體而言算平穩。<br />\n<br />\n現時虛銀有150億元存款，發放10億元貸款。他說，以往都有擔心市民對網絡銀行的接受程度，但過去一年經過疫情洗禮，市民的接受程度有所提高。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2377840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F2377840&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=56e06eab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2377840</a>"},{"pid":"7567ff0a23cf615b86765c57873f922725c2c784","tid":2394584,"uid":224882,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:31:28.000Z","msg":"咁我咪過主去外國開戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d8bcf95c12435d44ed9c5559b49e5ba75daa79","tid":2394584,"uid":282991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7567ff0a23cf615b86765c57873f922725c2c784","tid":2394584,"uid":224882,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:31:28.000Z","msg":"咁我咪過主去外國開戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"你平時係香港開戶用BNO?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23b3c37b22e6169fc6c5d6780f6fd0c0f45ae49","tid":2394584,"uid":224882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d8bcf95c12435d44ed9c5559b49e5ba75daa79","tid":2394584,"uid":282991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7567ff0a23cf615b86765c57873f9